title: Kerhallet (C. Ph. J.)
body: Kerhallet (C. Ph. J.) E.:Madère, les Iles Selvages et les Iles Canaries , Paris,1868 (Cartes et plans de la marine , n.° 267). A. le Gras collaborated on this work.

C. Ph. J. Kerhallet: Possible author or relevant figure related to the work on Madeira, Iles Selvages, and Iles Canaries.

1868: Publication of the work on Madeira, Iles Selvages, and Iles Canaries.
